{
  "stem": "10859.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to see where the grave is, just we wanted to see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And tragically, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we just couldn't stay there too long because we were just crying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ground was still shakin'.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe there were still a lot of people maybe were not dead yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We stayed there just for five minutes, and we left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, we didn't hear anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we decided, what are we going to do now?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we decided we're going to go and just live in the woods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The woods are big and large, deep for hundreds and hundreds of kilometer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went over there, and we find a place over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was not too far from-- some Polish man lived over there, not too far.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we figured, well, I don't know, maybe we'll try to make some contact with him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not all the people are bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not all are murderers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we walked in to him, and we told him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a Polish man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He lived by himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we says, we just survived from-- he says, I heard what happened, he says.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, all the surrounding areas knew that they killed the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he says, I would like to help you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, but what can I do for you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I say, would you allow us to sleep over there where you keep your cows and the horse in the barn-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A barn or whatever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, let us-- we're not going to stay there  in the daytime.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'll stay in the woods.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe at night when it gets cold, let us in over there to sleep over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was so nice, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
